entries.title: At least 68 killed in Nepal plane crash
entries.description: A Yeti Airlines flight carrying 72 passengers from Nepal’s capital Kathmandu crashed in the resort town of Pokhara, becoming Nepal’s worst air crash in three decades. At least 68 people were killed in the crash.
